    "role": "Credibility assessment team",
    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "Twelve of thirteen V&V 40 credibility factors meet or exceed required levels. The single gap (Test conditions, achieved 2 vs. required 3) is explicitly scoped: the COU is limited to static compression-bending per ASTM F1717, and the regulatory question does not require torsion or fatigue coverage at this stage. Validation metrics (E/uval < 1.96) and relative errors (<10%) satisfy pre-established acceptance criteria for all three QoIs across N=11 specimens from two independent laboratories. Overall credibility is sufficient to support an Accepted decision. Note: this package conforms to ProfileMinimal; digital signature is pending completion of the institutional signature workflow and has not been applied.",
